result.description:
This document describes the validation objectives, context, data required and criteria for acceptance. This will also contain a data procurement plan to ensure this validation. The validation does not address only data/products validation but are also meant for service validation. This document will contain the following volumes:
1. VR for Bathymetry determination from SAR imagery;
2. VR for Bathymetry, benthic classification and water quality determination from optical imagery;
3. VR for V essel detection with SAR;
4. VR for Time series processing for hyper temporal optical data analysis;
5. VR for Ocean and Coastal altimetry.
